      "writtenOn": "2017-11-28T22:09:04Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "It\u0027s a bit fuzzy to me. I\u0027m leaning more towards moving that out of mini_chromium and putting it in Crashpad, leaving only base/BUILD.gn in mini_chromium. I\u0027m becoming skeptical that a \"general\" GN configuration makes sense, and rather it should always be a per-project thing. It think it would necessitate a lot generality in the form of declare_args() or other extension and configuration points to handle different build switches/options/flavours. And it feels like we\u0027re not really in a position to create that hypothetical very-general configuration, having only a single consumer.\n\nAnyway, we can keep bashing on until we have a working trunk on a few platforms and maybe it\u0027ll be more clear either way by then.",
      "parentUuid": "a85599e4_30bebab8",
      "revId": "dea3454559b7354b03e4c0494c3aac3dd9817d78",
